{"tid":1842621,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【黃寧為玉碎 不作瓦全】黃台仰2020年同大家講話","createTime":"2020-01-25T19:55:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-13T23:44:51.000Z","uid":228437,"like":34,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"a9773010e62270d3765cf9fb49019791dad81f4c","tid":1842621,"uid":228437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T19:55:03.000Z","msg":"無人記得佢？點解無人講？<br />\n佢地本民前真係為左香港人付出好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">各位香港人，2020年喇。<br />\n我地既民主運動已經進行左廿幾年。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">由當年既陳巧文，梁天琦，黃台仰，<br />\n到今日有槍既蘇義士、斬何妖既董手足....</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">問問自己，我地到底失去左幾多手足，錯過左幾多次？</span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\"><br />\n2020年喇，懇求大家跑快啲，一齊努力，<br />\n而唔係係旁邊拍手、吶喊助威<br />\n一齊努力追上前線抗爭者既步伐。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MhiFRX4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMhiFRX4.png&h=747a5ff6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hknationwise/videos/2286169995014914/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhknationwise%2Fvideos%2F2286169995014914%2F&d=DF3UGDbnXTwcWfCLvBafJZLurRSHZiEGX9rhKonVocs%3D&h=3bf449a3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hknationwise/videos/2286169995014914/</a>"},{"pid":"a8d50d06b1e1f2c9a7314cfff43528459703c84e","tid":1842621,"uid":228437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T19:56:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"819a9eae62ae20cfe0d6c48a6ecc07723a815bc2","tid":1842621,"uid":228437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T19:56:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0797dd51e6a42d179205409e0511b38f4f9e2060","tid":1842621,"uid":230714,"like":13,"dis